  "instructions": [
    "In a large steamer basket, place the sliced ginger and fish.",
    "Steam the fish over boiling water for 8-10 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, prepare the noodles according to package instructions.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the gluten-free soy sauce and malt vinegar.",
    "Once the fish is cooked, remove it from the steamer and place it on a serving platter.",
    "Arrange the cooked noodles, bean sprouts, and sliced green onions on top of the fish.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately.",
    "Serve with sliced lime wedges and chili peppers on the side, if desired."
